INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_postmeta` VALUES (2477,170,'description','During the COVID-19, there are many people: the elderly, homeless, refugees, displaced workers, who need help with everyday activities and may be facing hardship and going hungry. We are providing food relief to the hungry. We are providing assistance to the elderly and others who cannot and should not venture out by assisting with essential services such as shopping for food and medicines. We are providing food packs to families whose lives and income have been disrupted by the COVID-19. We are providing financial support to the families of COVID-19 victims. As a community, we are all donating our time, talents and resources to bring hope and relief to our neighbors who need a helping hand in this time of crisis.');
